    <item>
      <title>墨西哥第四季度经济放缓幅度超出预期，关键降息成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/mexico-s-economy-slowed-more-than-expected-in-the-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于出口和家庭消费下降，墨西哥第四季度经济放缓幅度超过预期，引发了对该国央行将在未来几个月开始降息的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/mexico-s-economy-slowed-more-than-expected-in-the-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:11:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利因资本规则而看好美国银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/morgan-stanley-turns-bullish-on-us-banks-over-capital-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利分析师转而看好美国主要银行，因为他们预计即将进行的更高资本水平的监管改革将不会比当前提议那么繁重，从而为增加回购打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/morgan-stanley-turns-bullish-on-us-banks-over-capital-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
